sentence: what is the capital of the state with the lowest point ?
sentence-with-vars: what is the capital of the state with the lowest point ?
sql: select state.capital from state , highlow where state.state_name = highlow.state_name and highlow.lowest_elevation = ( select min ( highlow.lowest_elevation ) from highlow ) ;
sql-with-vars: select state.capital from state , highlow where state.state_name = highlow.state_name and highlow.lowest_elevation = ( select min ( highlow.lowest_elevation ) from highlow ) ;
